{
  "texts": [
    "We conduct limited analyses of aggregated employment categories based on publicly available data for a sample of consumer ChatGPT users.",
    "This sample included approximately 130,000 Free, Plus, and Pro users, and the employment categories were aggregated by a vendor working through a secure Data Clean Room (DCR).",
    "For this analysis, we use the same exclusion criteria as for the message-level datasets: we exclude deactivated users, banned users, users who have opted out of training, and users whose self-reported age is under 18.",
    "Because the data was only available for a subset of users the results may not be representative of the full pool of users.",
    "Description."
  ]
}